  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0d85\u0db4\u0dd2-\u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dda-\u0d85\u0dba-\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4-\u0dba\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dca\u0dc0\u0da7--\u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca-\u0dc0\u0d9c-\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1-\u0d95\u0db1/11-396815",
  "time_ut": 1662018732,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db4\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d85\u0dba \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0dba\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dca\u0dc0\u0da7  \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0d9c \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d95\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The people should be held accountable for sending people like us to parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Kumara Welgama said that politicians, officials as well as the people should be held accountable for the state the country has fallen into. He said this while joining the budget debate in Parliament.",
        "\"Even we don't beat Matia to get caught. Even in a company, taxes are still being evaded. Now it is said that a Rajapaksa bought a house worth 40 crores. Someone find this. If this is found, the Rajapaksas will be sent home forever.",
        "We all have to work voluntarily to get the country out of its fallen state. We should all support the government.",
        "Remember that I am not going to the government. Otherwise, I think he is trying to get this ministry. I don't want ministry. He was without a minister for 7 years.",
        "Even if I lose the ministership, people from our side treat me like the Chief Minister. Let's lift this net together.",
        "Not only the politicians but also the officials should be held accountable for this. The public should also be held accountable for this. Because the people should be responsible for sending our people to the parliament. Need to change next time. It will not change.\""
      ],
